   United States Department of Transportation



                                 Our Mission

     To ensure that the Department is in compliance with government-wide
     executive orders, laws, regulations, and guidelines that relate to
     internal management issues within the Department and to improve and
     promote departmental leadership, direction, and partnerships in
     security and administrative management with the operating
     administrations including the Office of the Secretary and TASC.

                  DOT Internal Management Policy Authority

     DOT 1000.17  ADMINISTRATIVE SERVICE POLICY FUNCTIONS

